 mutate(
   death_rate = (total_deaths / population) * 100,
   case_rate = (total_cases / population) * 100
 )

data collection and cleaning of Asia

tt <- asia_data$total_tests
N <- length(tt)
tt_s <- numeric(N)
tt_s[1] <- 0
for (i in 2:N) {
  tt_s[i] = tt[i]
  if (tt[i] == 0) {
    if (asia_data$location[i] == asia_data$location[i - 1]){
      tt_s[i] = tt_s[i - 1]
    }
  }
}
asia_data["total_tests_smoothed"] <- tt_s

data cleaning

tt <- asia_data$total_tests
pv <- asia_data$people_vaccinated
pfv <- asia_data$people_fully_vaccinated
tv <- asia_data$total_vaccinations
tb <- asia_data$total_boosters

N <- length(tt)

tt_s <- numeric(N)
pv_s <- numeric(N)
pfv_s <- numeric(N)
tv_s <- numeric(N)
tb_s <- numeric(N)

tt_s[1] <- 0
pv_s[1] <- 0
pfv_s[1] <- 0
tv_s[1] <- 0
tb_s[1] <- 0

for (i in 2:N) {
  tt_s[i] = tt[i]
  if (tt[i] == 0) {
    if (asia_data$location[i] == asia_data$location[i - 1]) {
      tt_s[i] = tt_s[i - 1]
    }
  }

  pv_s[i] = pv[i]
  if (pv[i] == 0) {
    if (asia_data$location[i] == asia_data$location[i - 1]) {
      pv_s[i] = pv_s[i - 1]
    }
  }

  pfv_s[i] = pfv[i]
  if (pfv[i] == 0) {
    if (asia_data$location[i] == asia_data$location[i - 1]) {
      pfv_s[i] = pfv_s[i - 1]
    }
  }

  tv_s[i] = tv[i]
  if (tv[i] == 0) {
    if (asia_data$location[i] == asia_data$location[i - 1]) {
      tv_s[i] = tv_s[i - 1]
    }
  }

  tb_s[i] = tb[i]
  if (tb[i] == 0) {
    if (asia_data$location[i] == asia_data$location[i - 1]) {
      tb_s[i] = tb_s[i - 1]
    }
  }
}

asia_data["total_tests"] <- tt_s
asia_data["people_vaccinated"] <- pv_s
asia_data["people_fully_vaccinated"] <- pfv_s
asia_data["total_vaccinations_smoothed"] <- tv_s
asia_data["total_boosters_smoothed"] <- tb_s

df <- asia_data %>%
  group_by(date) %>%
  summarize(
    total_case = sum(total_cases),
    new_case = sum(new_cases),
    total_death = sum(total_deaths),
    new_death = sum(new_deaths),
    hos_patient = sum(hosp_patients),
    icu_patient = sum(icu_patients),
    total_test = sum(total_tests_smoothed),
    new_test_smoothed = sum(new_tests_smoothed),

    people_fully_vaccinated = sum(people_fully_vaccinated), 
    total_booster = sum(total_boosters_smoothed),
    new_vaccinations_smoothed = sum(new_vaccinations_smoothed),
    new_people_vaccinated_smoothed = sum(new_people_vaccinated_smoothed),
    excess_mortality = sum(excess_mortality),
    excess_mortality_cumulative = sum(excess_mortality_cumulative),
    excess_mortality_cumulative_absolute = sum(excess_mortality_cumulative_absolute),

library(dplyr)

asia_data <- asia_data %>%
  mutate(
    stringency_phase = case_when(
      stringency_index <= 30 ~ "Ordinary",
      stringency_index > 30 & stringency_index <= 60 ~ "Serious",
      stringency_index > 60 ~ "Severe"
    )
  )

asia_data <- asia_data[!is.na(asia_data$stringency_phase) & !is.infinite(asia_data$stringency_phase), ]

df <- df %>%
  left_join(asia_data %>% select(date, stringency_phase), by = "date")

ggplot(df, aes(x = as.Date(date))) +
